{"tid":767890,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"茶記/大快活早餐D鯰魚柳真係難食到屌晒老母","createTime":"2018-08-05T02:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T05:08:26.000Z","uid":119385,"like":9,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6836c9abf3130271553ea77fe0221850ffe4ba","tid":767890,"uid":119385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/104914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F104914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f0f68481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1511029/%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E5%BA%97%E9%AD%9A%E6%9F%B3%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E9%AD%9A%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1511029%2F%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%25AD%259A%25E6%259F%25B3%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2594%259A%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E9%25AD%259A%25EF%25BC%259F&d=%2FyshlLpn4ccxj6cNBwbS8S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6d0efbb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1511029/%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E5%BA%97%E9%AD%9A%E6%9F%B3%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9A%E9%BA%BC%E9%AD%9A%EF%BC%9F</a><br />\n<br />\nD食肆成撚日貪平入貨<br />\n又用黎扮龍脷柳/班塊<br />\n其實食落口真係有陣臭味, 好撚難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要食魚柳肯定食大家樂早餐果隻鱈魚柳 (只限早餐, 午晚市大家樂都用鯰魚柳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541b3af588d0ef9b06de14d99d7c47ae1f2acaca","tid":767890,"uid":36296,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"大家樂都開始請打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713c0d3ae333654d4937c9274abaec7ac5cd9106","tid":767890,"ui